data.description: Welcome home to Lago Mar! This incredible two-story home sits on over a half an acre corner lot in the highly sought after Kellam High School District! Walking in you are greeted with a sitting room and dining room on either side of the staircase before entering the living room. The large adjacent kitchen features an eat at island topped with elegant quartz. The cozy sunroom provides floor to ceiling views of the vast, fully fenced back yard with an expansive deck and Gunite pool! You will find one bedroom, a separate full bath, an office, and laundry room all off the two car side load garage! Upstairs includes three bedrooms, primary ensuite with ample storage and separate access to the FROG which can be used as a multi-use space or a 6th Bedroom! Just minutes to Sandbridge Beaches and nearby bases, you don’t want to miss this Retreat by the Beach! Upgrades within past 3 years include new fireplace lining, Dual HVAC, Water Softner, Pool pump, and tankless gas water heater.
